  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bc0\u0b9a\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0bb5\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bae\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Strong winds likely - Department of Meteorology",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Department of Meteorology, there will be several spells of rain in Upper, Sabaragamuwa and North-West provinces and in Nuwara Eliya, Kandy, Galle and Matara districts.",
        "The western slopes of Madhya Pradesh and North, North Central and North Western Provinces and Trincomalee and Ambandottai districts may experience gusty winds of up to 50 kmph from time to time.",
        "There will be light rain over coastal areas from Puttalam through Colombo and Galle to Matara.",
        "Wind will blow from South-West direction with wind speed of 30-40 kmph. The wind speed may increase to 50-60 kmph in coastal areas from Puttalam to Trincomalee via Mannar and Kangesanthurai and from Matara to Pottuvil via Ambandottai.",
        "From Puttalam to Trincomalee via Mannar and Kangesanthurai and from Matara to Pothuvill via Ambandottai, the sea surface will be turbulent from time to time. Other sea surfaces around the island can be quite rough from time to time."
      ],
